FLORA OF Alabama
Clay County
Creek Farm
*Galax aphylla*

Areas of this evergreen plant were scattered on a steep slope
or bluff on White Oak Creek. They seem to prefer to be near a
large stone which were usually near.

Gloyce C. Howell                                       21-6-1997
